ox-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/5b83e4940ebe5418456cc5d7929774a7" alt="" /> <img src="http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/5b83e4940ebe5418456cc5d7929774a7?s=100&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="100" height="100" alt="" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 photo avatar-default" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Lorenzo Bassi"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/lorenzo-bassi/">View all articles by Lorenzo Bassi</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/11/serata-inaugurale-della-novecentesca-stagione-sinfonica-del-teatro-la-fenice/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Serata inaugurale della novecentesca Stagione sinfonica del Teatro La Fenice</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/11/opera-de-marseillela-straniera/" rel="next">Opra de Marseille:&#8221;La Straniera&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2013/11/philhadelphia-operasvadba-wedding/#respond" 